## Discover
* **Work.** View my LinkedIn profile [@csmattjohnston](https://pk.linkedin.com/in/csmattjohnston)
* **Experience.** Download my updated [Resume](https://www.dropbox.com/s/4rgyn338sv58qt5/Resume.pdf?dl=0)
* **Code.** View my contribution to Github [@csmattjohnston](http://www.github.com/csmattjohnston)
* **Posts.** Follow my posts on Facebook [@jmattfoo](https://www.facebook.com/jmattfoo)
* **My Daily Life.** Follow and view photos of my travel adventures with friends [@Mattfue](https://www.instagram.com/mattfue/)
* **Languages.** Currently learning Korean, Italian, Mandarin and Arabic


## Projects in Progress
* [Exercise App](http://www.github.com/csmattjohnston/iOSExerciseApp/). An iOS Exercise app created to decrease obesity with a companion
* [Music Studio Application](http://www.github.com/csmattjohnston/MusicStudio/). A Java music making program created similar to GarageBand or Fruity Loops Studio
* [Trauma Cat](http://www.github.com/csmattjohnston/TraumaCat/). An iOS medical app created to track patient information and to do lists
* [Practice Problems](http://www.github.com/csmattjohnston/ExerciseProblems/). My solutions to various online data structures and algorithm problems
